title: Texas Flip and Move S02E05 Houseboat vs. Bayou Shack PDTV.x264-J
description:
Texas Flip and Move - Season 2, Episode 5




Captain Cody and the Houseboat of Horrors vs. Randy's Bayou Shack

Cody and Suzi are on their way to an auction when Cody impulsively buys a houseboat. Randy wins a building at auction that looks like it had been used as a roadside fruit stand but he discovers it has no bedroom or bathroom. He decides to go with a rustic-look 'Bayou Shack'.




Original Air Date: 16-Oct-2015
